### File with variable definitions

@base_url = https://api.example.com
@api_version = v1
@auth_token = abc123xyz789

### Request using file variables
GET {{base_url}}/{{api_version}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Request using file variables and defining a new variable
@user_id = 12345

GET {{base_url}}/{{api_version}}/users/{{user_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Multiple variable definitions in sequence
@host = api.example.com
@port = 8080
@protocol = https

### Request using the variables defined above
GET {{protocol}}://{{host}}:{{port}}/status
